{"tid":1912103,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"催生亞洲新供應鏈？美科技巨頭想將零件生產線移至東南亞","createTime":"2020-03-05T21:49:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-06T01:10:16.000Z","uid":141151,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"91c21cbe4c18381acd50c8574454fb48eca0c2ab","tid":1912103,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T21:49:01.000Z","msg":"催生亞洲新供應鏈？美科技巨頭想將零件生產線移至東南亞<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3089275\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3089275&d=%2FrzxgVsCSRBeEmt1flTkcCL1bdbhbSvxCnYHZ8iA0HE%3D&h=c4539cd4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3089275&h=30ebb52d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3089275</a><br />\n<br />\n〔財經頻道／綜合報導〕武漢肺炎（COVID-19）疫情影響中國經濟，全球供應鏈出現裂痕，美國科技巨頭蘋果（Apple）、谷歌（Google）和微軟（Microsoft）試圖想將零件的生產線轉移至亞洲其他國家。<br />\n<br />\n綜合媒體報導，中國身為世界工廠，為因應疫情工廠停擺，導致供應鏈中斷，蘋果、谷歌和微軟開始向外尋求，試圖將其零件的生產線，轉移至亞洲其他國家，像是泰國及越南。<br />\n<br />\n《日經亞洲評論》提到，4月開始，谷歌將在越南生產低成本智慧型手機，包含另外1款旗艦型手機，亦會在下半年生產，同時，谷歌還要求泰國的合作夥伴，準備好智能家居產品的生產線。此外，微軟希望其第2代筆記型電腦的Surface系列在越南開始生產。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，蘋果去年也試圖在越南對AirPods的生產進行試驗，並要求供應商考慮將15％到30％的生產，從中國轉移到東南亞的其他地區。<br />\n<br />\n不過，報導也指出，有鑑於在中國的零件生產線已根深蒂固，加上要在另1個地區建立產能，也需要時間，種種因素都顯示，要將零件生產線轉移到中國之外是相當困難的。"},{"pid":"9d79aa81a9077ca8b007bf500516f0e6d5fe2674","tid":1912103,"uid":199957,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"91c21cbe4c18381acd50c8574454fb48eca0c2ab","tid":1912103,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T21:49:01.000Z","msg":"催生亞洲新供應鏈？美科技巨頭想將零件生產線移至東南亞<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3089275\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3089275&d=%2FrzxgVsCSRBeEmt1flTkcCL1bdbhbSvxCnYHZ8iA0HE%3D&h=c4539cd4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3089275&h=30ebb52d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3089275</a><br />\n<br />\n〔財經頻道／綜合報導〕武漢肺炎（COVID-19）疫情影響中國經濟，全球供應鏈出現裂痕，美國科技巨頭蘋果（Apple）、谷歌（Google）和微軟（Microsoft）試圖想將零件的生產線轉移至亞洲其他國家。<br />\n<br />\n綜合媒體報導，中國身為世界工廠，為因應疫情工廠停擺，導致供應鏈中斷，蘋果、谷歌和微軟開始向外尋求，試圖將其零件的生產線，轉移至亞洲其他國家，像是泰國及越南。<br />\n<br />\n《日經亞洲評論》提到，4月開始，谷歌將在越南生產低成本智慧型手機，包含另外1款旗艦型手機，亦會在下半年生產，同時，谷歌還要求泰國的合作夥伴，準備好智能家居產品的生產線。此外，微軟希望其第2代筆記型電腦的Surface系列在越南開始生產。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，蘋果去年也試圖在越南對AirPods的生產進行試驗，並要求供應商考慮將15％到30％的生產，從中國轉移到東南亞的其他地區。<br />\n<br />\n不過，報導也指出，有鑑於在中國的零件生產線已根深蒂固，加上要在另1個地區建立產能，也需要時間，種種因素都顯示，要將零件生產線轉移到中國之外是相當困難的。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T22:11:07.000Z","msg":"侵講撚左幾耐<br />\n你班仆街而家先換地方"},{"pid":"252750a674451d7899b75d11201e2df7f1441d63","tid":1912103,"uid":41343,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T23:43:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2020/01/08/tesla-model-3-100-percent-made-in-china/life-tech/auto/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2020%2F01%2F08%2Ftesla-model-3-100-percent-made-in-china%2Flife-tech%2Fauto%2F&d=%2FrzxgVsCSRBeEmt1flTkcCL1bdbhbSvxCnYHZ8iA0HE%3D&h=e6853f20\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2020/01/08/tesla-model-3-100-percent-made-in-china/life-tech/auto/</a><br />\n<br />\nTesla 有冇後悔all in China"},{"pid":"2b6d613570907755a615f9eb2d3477674c7b854b","tid":1912103,"uid":167394,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"252750a674451d7899b75d11201e2df7f1441d63","tid":1912103,"uid":41343,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T23:43:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2020/01/08/tesla-model-3-100-percent-made-in-china/life-tech/auto/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2020%2F01%2F08%2Ftesla-model-3-100-percent-made-in-china%2Flife-tech%2Fauto%2F&d=%2FrzxgVsCSRBeEmt1flTkcCL1bdbhbSvxCnYHZ8iA0HE%3D&h=e6853f20\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2020/01/08/tesla-model-3-100-percent-made-in-china/life-tech/auto/</a><br />\n<br />\nTesla 有冇後悔all in China"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T23:45:49.000Z","msg":"無<br />\n因為全部由大陸借出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85bcb4a7c74fa7dee384d1177fc34682a377bbe2","tid":1912103,"uid":31186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T00:19:39.000Z","msg":"去中心化"},{"pid":"5568475d9b094cb485728b67ca90766e80e28036","tid":1912103,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T00:43:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1595f6685530df219b8922f48cd82ec48c3ebede","tid":1912103,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T00:44:03.000Z","msg":"遲做好過唔做"},{"pid":"df2124fb78c16e8eb5c745c4d471d18f282479cb","tid":1912103,"uid":44358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T00:52:21.000Z","msg":"未來唔係將生產線搬走，而係搬返自己國家，再用自動化減成本。"},{"pid":"c9d50eef8208cb7e795aa90358e2eb5b84079933","tid":1912103,"uid":82929,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"91c21cbe4c18381acd50c8574454fb48eca0c2ab","tid":1912103,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T21:49:01.000Z","msg":"催生亞洲新供應鏈？美科技巨頭想將零件生產線移至東南亞<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3089275\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3089275&d=%2FrzxgVsCSRBeEmt1flTkcCL1bdbhbSvxCnYHZ8iA0HE%3D&h=c4539cd4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3089275&h=30ebb52d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3089275</a><br />\n<br />\n〔財經頻道／綜合報導〕武漢肺炎（COVID-19）疫情影響中國經濟，全球供應鏈出現裂痕，美國科技巨頭蘋果（Apple）、谷歌（Google）和微軟（Microsoft）試圖想將零件的生產線轉移至亞洲其他國家。<br />\n<br />\n綜合媒體報導，中國身為世界工廠，為因應疫情工廠停擺，導致供應鏈中斷，蘋果、谷歌和微軟開始向外尋求，試圖將其零件的生產線，轉移至亞洲其他國家，像是泰國及越南。<br />\n<br />\n《日經亞洲評論》提到，4月開始，谷歌將在越南生產低成本智慧型手機，包含另外1款旗艦型手機，亦會在下半年生產，同時，谷歌還要求泰國的合作夥伴，準備好智能家居產品的生產線。此外，微軟希望其第2代筆記型電腦的Surface系列在越南開始生產。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，蘋果去年也試圖在越南對AirPods的生產進行試驗，並要求供應商考慮將15％到30％的生產，從中國轉移到東南亞的其他地區。<br />\n<br />\n不過，報導也指出，有鑑於在中國的零件生產線已根深蒂固，加上要在另1個地區建立產能，也需要時間，種種因素都顯示，要將零件生產線轉移到中國之外是相當困難的。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T01:00:54.000Z","msg":"發夢啦<br />\n東南亞冇人願意放棄自己環境<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />幫你班資本家整平貨<br />\n<br />\n要平貨就返支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ea1b12b3e947bc817de0386d066762e408f265d","tid":1912103,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T01:05:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />入左黎想走"},{"pid":"2a2ce5c7995022faea751824672148409cbf0b51","tid":1912103,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T01:10:16.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}